136
00:18:21,648 --> 00:18:26,152
<i>Here is important information about how
this debilitating disease will affect you.</i>

137
00:18:26,252 --> 00:18:29,555
<i>And how you can manage it responsibly
before eventual containment</i>

138
00:18:29,655 --> 00:18:34,249
<i>at the defective emotional
neuropathy facility, the den.</i>

139
00:18:35,093 --> 00:18:38,214
<i>Switched On Syndrome
is a malfunction of the gene silencing</i>

140
00:18:38,314 --> 00:18:41,868
<i>that controls human emotions
and eliminates human flaws.</i>

141
00:18:41,968 --> 00:18:46,272
<i>But in Switched On Syndrome, problem
genes lose their silencing and re-awaken.</i>

142
00:18:46,372 --> 00:18:51,611
