153
00:19:24,026 --> 00:19:27,180
<i>consistent low level emotion
and emotional volatility,</i>

154
00:19:27,280 --> 00:19:29,081
<i>these symptoms will worsen.</i>

155
00:19:29,181 --> 00:19:32,285
<i>In stage four, acute behavioral chaos,</i>

156
00:19:32,385 --> 00:19:35,455
<i>you will no longer function as
a productive member of the Collective.</i>

157
00:19:35,555 --> 00:19:38,191
<i>And your doctor will prescribe
containment at the den.</i>

158
00:19:38,291 --> 00:19:40,693
<i>Where you will be provided
with electro restraint,</i>

159
00:19:40,793 --> 00:19:44,963
<i>emotional suppression,
and a pain-free death scenario.</i>

160
00:19:45,063 --> 00:19:47,267
<i>If you have questions
about your condition,</i>

161
00:19:47,367 --> 00:19:51,170
<i>notify your doctor or health and safety
official for immediate attention.</i>

162
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:54,763
<i>And remember,
a cure is right around the corner.</i>

163
