287
00:40:31,342 --> 00:40:33,549
Hello, Leonard.

288
00:40:33,944 --> 00:40:35,785
Silas.

289
00:40:36,747 --> 00:40:40,222
I didn't expect to see you here this late.

290
00:40:43,687 --> 00:40:46,957
Have you thought about killing yourself?

291
00:40:47,057 --> 00:40:50,366
No, that's not until stage three.

292
00:40:56,133 --> 00:40:58,908
Why is Nia's interface on?

293
00:41:00,738 --> 00:41:03,846
