303
00:41:35,372 --> 00:41:37,541
to health and safety.

304
00:41:37,641 --> 00:41:41,183
Unless, of course,
the activity were to stop.

305
00:41:42,546 --> 00:41:44,620
Does that make sense to you?

306
00:41:47,051 --> 00:41:48,553
Yes.

307
00:41:49,053 --> 00:41:50,888
Good.

308
00:41:51,538 --> 00:41:53,947
