309
00:42:36,834 --> 00:42:39,842
- Goodnight.
- Goodnight, Nia.

310
00:43:23,113 --> 00:43:25,254
He knows.

311
00:43:28,285 --> 00:43:30,760
What are we going to do?

312
00:43:36,226 --> 00:43:39,068
